## 10. Base de Données

### Migrations principales

**users** : id, name, email, password (hashed), monthly_income_target, onboarding_completed

**wallets** : id, user_id (FK), name, balance (decimal:2), currency (XOF), type (cash/mobile_money/bank), is_default

**categories** : id, name, icon, color, type (income/expense), is_system, user_id (FK nullable)

**transactions** : id, user_id (FK), category_id (FK nullable), wallet_id (FK), type (income/expense/transfer), amount (decimal:2), description, transaction_date, source (manual/sms_wave/sms_orange_money/api), external_id (index), status (pending/completed/cancelled)

**budgets** : id, user_id (FK), category_id (FK), amount (decimal:2), period (daily/weekly/monthly/yearly), start_date, end_date, spent (decimal:2), is_active

**financial_goals** : id, user_id (FK), name, description, target_amount (decimal:2), current_amount (decimal:2), target_date, icon, color, status (pending/in_progress/completed), category_id (FK), reminder_frequency, last_reminder_sent_at

**parsed_sms** : id, user_id (FK), provider, raw_content, parsed_amount (decimal:2), parsed_phone, parsed_type, transaction_id (FK nullable), status (pending/processed/failed/ignored), error_message, parsed_at

**alerts** : id, user_id (FK), type, title, message, data (JSON), is_read, read_at

